title: #169: Blacklanta (@ComedienneMsPat, @BigJayOakerson)
itunes:title: Blacklanta with Ms. Pat and Big Jay Oakerson
description: Ms. Pat joined me in a park in Brooklyn (maybe Park Slope? No, that seems wrong) to tell me about what it was like growing up in the hood in Atlanta. Spoiler alert: It was way different than how I grew up in the suburbs of Maryland. It's a story of teen pregnancies, gunshot wounds, and Jimmy Carter.
